    "Management": {
      "text": "Supportive management (treat volume overload)\nSodium and water restriction\nFurosemide\n(also controls hypertension)\nACEi\nor\nCCBs\nfor hypertension not controlled by diuretics\n[1]\nConsider\ndialysis\n(for acute\nrenal failure\n)",
